          <h2 i18n:translate="">Jurisdiction</h2>
          <p i18n:translate="">The agreement is construed in accordance with and is subject to German law. Place of fullfilment is Augsburg, Germany. Place of jurisdiction is Augsburg, Germany.</p>
        </div>
  
